name: napari-plot-profile
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "napari-plot-profile" %}
{% set version = "0.2.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/napari-plot-profile-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e4c309027b177473f9a63186f36343529e09e0db7bb779ec6a9a4be2c270d894

build:
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 0

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.7
  run:
    - napari
    - napari-plugin-engine >=0.1.4
    - napari-skimage-regionprops >=0.2.4
    - napari-tools-menu
    - numpy
    - pyqtgraph
    - python >=3.7

test:
  imports:
    - napari_plot_profile
  commands:
    - pip list
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/haesleinhuepf/napari-plot-profile
  summary: Plot intensity along a line in napari
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - goanpeca
    - jaimergp
    - haesleinhuepf
